    </div>


    <h5>Decimal</h5>
    <p>
        Decimal is simply the Numeral System of base 10. Decimal is the standard numbering system used by most of the world which consists of numbers with digits from 0 to 9. Decimal counting is how a person would typically count.
    </p>

